37412>>>        //  Hide header & apply nice background style
37412>>>        Send HideHeader to ghoWebApp
37413>>>        WebSet psCSSClass of ghoWebApp to "LoginBackground"
37414>>>    End_Procedure
37415>>>    
37415>>>End_Object
