38482>>>>>    Procedure SetActionButtons
38485>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
38485>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
38485>>>>>        Boolean bHasRecord
38485>>>>>        Handle hoDD
38485>>>>>
38485>>>>>        Get Server to hoDD
38486>>>>>        Get GetNavigateData to NavigateData
38487>>>>>        Get HasRecord of hoDD to bHasRecord
38488>>>>>
38488>>>>>        // let's hide all buttons and then Show the ones we want
38488>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to False
38489>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to False
38490>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to False
38491>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to False
38492>>>>>
38492>>>>>        If (NavigateData.bReadOnly) Begin
38494>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to True
38495>>>>>        End
38495>>>>>>
38495>>>>>        Else Begin
38496>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to True
38497>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to True
38498>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to bHasRecord
38499>>>>>        End
38499>>>>>>
38499>>>>>    End_Procedure
